item.title: Has anyone noticed
item.dc:creator: @n33bz0rpl0x `Aaron
item.description:
@n33bz0rpl0x wrote:

Pking was a very important thing for me to do in Runescape, it’s how i trained, how i made friends, how i thought of ways to become better and do more quests to better my character, it was extremely rare when i was outside the wilderness. Yeah HD took away that old feeling, and it sucked, i used to get up every morning when i was <13 and get a cup of coffee, chop yews in F2P or go pking, i used to give my best friend on Runescape a set of full rune every year, and he used to give me items as-well, we cannot even give a gift in Runescape now for Christ’s sake, what is done is done, but i don’t enjoy it anymore.

Read full topic
